      <guid>https://alexandervossen.github.io/post/2022-03-28-conferences/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;new-year-new-conference-season&#34;&gt;New year, new conference season!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My recent study with Stephie has been accepted at the SASE 2022 and the AOM 2022 Annual Conference! If you want to meet up in beautiful Amsterdam and/or Seattle make sure to drop me a mail!&lt;/p&gt;
